*********************************************************************
1) webcamd requires the cuse4bsd kernel module, please load this
by doing

       # kldload cuse4bsd

or adding

       cuse4bsd_load="YES"

to your /boot/loader.conf.

2) add webcamd_enable="YES"

to your /etc/rc.conf

3) Please restart devd as the configuration changed

	# service devd restart

*********************************************************************
